data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Beaumont's desirable west end! This spacious and inviting property boasts 4 bedrooms and3 bathrooms, providing ample space for your family's comfort and needs. You'll be greeted by a grand living room featuring tall ceilings that create an airy and open atmosphere. The centerpiece of the living room is a charming wood-burning fireplace. The well-designed layout includes a bonus room that offers versatile possibilities – whether you envision a home office, a playroom, or even a private gym, this space can easily be tailored to your lifestyle. For those who love to cook and entertain, the large kitchen will be a true delight with granite countertops and an abundance of cabinets. The yard itself offers plenty of space for gardening, play, and your furry friends to roam freely. The location in Beaumont's west end ensures you're well-connected to shopping, dining, and entertainment options.
